Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:37.25,EDCN - ep12,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur8}你溫柔的聲音也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:39.67,EDCN - ep12,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur8}你愛哭的習慣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:41.72,EDCN - ep12,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur8}每多了解你一點
