Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:50.81,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我會盡力的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:55.81,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,不要做危險的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.16,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我會盡力的
